ecr_repository_uri.description: ECR repository URI (used by CI to push images).

acm_certificate_arn.description: ACM certificate ARN for HTTPS listener (required if enable_https=true).

allowed_ingress_cidrs.description: CIDR blocks allowed to access the ALB on HTTP/HTTPS.

container_image.description: Full container image URI (including tag) to run in ECS. If empty, defaults to <ecr_repository_url>:latest.

container_port.description: Container port exposed by the application.

desired_count.description: Number of ECS tasks to run.

ecr_repository_name.description: ECR repository name used by CI and runtime.

enable_https.description: Enable HTTPS listener. Requires ACM certificate ARN.

health_check_path.description: ALB target group health check path. App serves '/' so default is '/'.

project_name.description: Project/name prefix used for resource naming.
